  "texts": [
    "We pre-processed a dataset consisting of 24 distinct colorectal image classes to ensure the quality and consistency of the input data.",
    "Standardisation of the images that will be input into the model is the initial step in the process of generating a dependable dataset.",
    "The subsequent stage is normalization, which involves the equalization of pixel intensity levels to facilitate the quicker and simpler training of the neural network.",
    "Furthermore, we implement data augmentation techniques such as tilting, rotation, and scaling to expand the sample datasets and improve the model's resilience to shift and orientation changes.",
    "We employ noise reduction filters to eliminate artefacts and improve images."
